description:
There's no better way to blend in to your surroundings than by wearing Realtree camo, no matter where you hunt or enjoy the outdoors. Realtree is the home of world's most versatile camouflage patterns.

Get your Palm ready for the stand with these officially licensed Realtree patterns.

Updates:
- Added support for Pixi-specific wallpapers.
- All new code, all new UI.
- Twice as many wallpapers.

***Please note that this app requires a WiFi or 3G connection to work properly. It may take a few seconds to load each wallpaper from the server. Please be patient as you scroll through the wallpapers.***
